this evening, marking the first step toward the party=E2=80=99s goal of sec=
uring major tax and spending cuts. Still, House Speaker Mike Johnson should=
n=E2=80=99t relax just yet. This was the easy part.

As always, Johnson=E2=80=99s largest obstacle was his razor-thin majority: =
He could afford to lose just one Republican
