e earlier this year, Trump successfully flipped two holdouts. He didn=E2=80=
=99t bother with Massie.)

But actually turning this framework=E2=80=94the most ambitious Republican t=
ax and spending cuts effort since at least the Gingrich era=E2=80=94into re=
ality will still require numerous rounds of legislating. The Appropriations=
